('ea9e3c58-588d-5a9e-8928-08b9a4d215a3', 3, 'successor_check_live_fetch', 'positive', NULL, 'Live team page at https://www.primetxsurveys.com/ (fetched 2026-05-16). primetxsurveys.com homepage (live-fetch): Houston HQ at 2417 North Fwy 77009; second office in Mission TX 78573; serves Houston, Rockport, Rio Grande Valley; ''Order a Survey'' online flow exists; ''Request a Free Quote''; modern site, copyright 2026. Services: residential, commercial, real-estate, boundary, acreage/lot, topographic, elevation cert, ALTA/ACSM, platting/replatting, builder services. References ''25 years of experience''. NO individual RPLS named on site.', 'live_website_fetch', 'https://www.primetxsurveys.com/', '2026-05-16'),
('ea9e3c58-588d-5a9e-8928-08b9a4d215a3', 1, 'a_tier_deep_dive_completed', 'positive', NULL, 'Deep-dive outcome: passed_a_with_caveats. Items checked: 1_owner_age: Richard V. Hall est age ~78 (RPLS granted 1978 + 30 age + 18 = ~78). License-tenure proxy. OV65 not verified.; 2_successor_verification: PASSED — primetxsurveys.com live-fetch (2026-05-16): no individual RPLS named on site; Richard V. Hall is presumed-sole RPLS per TBPELS. Multi-office (Houston HQ + Mission TX) but single RPLS-of-recor; 3_comptroller_status: Operating per current website + 2026 copyright + ''Order a Survey'' online flow + ''Request a Free Quote'' active.; 4_disciplinary: No disciplinary action surfaced.; 5_civil_filings: None surfaced.; 6_building_ownership: Houston HQ 2417 North Fwy Houston 77009 — North Loop location, urban infill. CAD verification pending.; 7_value_add_thesis: (See sharpened.) Modernized website + online ordering = above-baseline tech-stack; but capacity-bound by single RPLS.; 8_metro_pull: Greater Houston (Harris County) + Mission TX (Hidalgo) + Rockport (Aransas) + Rio Grande Valley footprint = multi-metro Texas coverage. Houston subsidence monitoring + coastal-flood FEMA elev cert wor', 'phase_5_a_tier_deep_dive', NULL, '2026-05-16'),
